Privacy Policy
Privacy Policy
Last Updated: Feb 1 2025
Remote Sunrise LTD (“we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal data. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your data when you use our website and mobile applications (“Services”). By using our Services, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
Data We Collect We collect only anonymous data in the form of analytics and crash reports. This data helps us improve the functionality and performance of our Services. We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) such as your name, email, or payment details.
How We Use Your Data The anonymous data we collect is used solely for improving our Services. This includes monitoring performance, identifying technical issues, and enhancing user experience.
Data Sharing We do not share your data with third parties except as necessary for processing crash reports or analytics. This information is anonymized and cannot be linked to specific individuals.
Payment Processing Payments for in-app purchases or other services offered through our mobile applications are processed by Apple. We do not handle any payment details or personal information related to transactions. Apple’s privacy policy governs the handling of your payment data.
Data Retention We retain your data for as long as needed to provide and improve our Services. Anonymous data may be stored indefinitely for the purposes mentioned above. However, we do not store personal data since none is collected.
Security We take reasonable precautions to protect the data we collect from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
Your Rights Since we do not collect personally identifiable information, there are no specific rights related to data access, correction, or deletion. If we ever collect personal data in the future, we will inform you and comply with applicable laws regarding your rights.
Governing Law This Privacy Policy shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of Israel.
Changes to This Privacy Policy We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on our website or within the app, and the updated version will be effective as of the date posted. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.
Contact Us If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at support@rs.ltd
